OL,3,CReeves promises more than #13bn for
OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FDuring the announcement, the
OL,8,Fchancellor accused the Conservatives
OL,9,Fof not setting aside any money to pay
OL,10,Ffor the compensation saying: "The
OL,11,FLeader of the Opposition rightly made
OL,12,Fan unequivocal apology for the
OL,13,Finjustice of the infected blood
OL,14,Fscandal on behalf of the British
OL,15,Fstate... but he did not budget for the
OL,16,Fcosts of compensation."
OL,18,FShe said the announcement is "long
OL,19,Foverdue for the pain and injustice
OL,20,Fthat they have suffered."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
