OL,3,CReeves promises more than #13bn for
OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FThe handling of the compensation
OL,8,Fschemes for both scandals has been
OL,9,Fcriticised by victims and campaigners
OL,10,Ffor taking too long.
OL,12,FPost Office CEO Nick Read told the
OL,13,FHorizon Inquiry earlier this month he
OL,14,Ffelt "deep regret" over how the
OL,15,Fcompensation had been handled.
OL,17,FEarlier this week ITV News reported
OL,18,FParliament would launch an inquiry
OL,19,Finto the delays in providing the
OL,20,Fcompensation to subpostmasters.
