OL,3,CReeves promises more than #13bn for
OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FBetween 1999 and 2015, more than 700
OL,8,FPost Office sub-postmasters were
OL,9,Fconvicted of theft or false accounting
OL,10,Fand thousands more were forced to make
OL,11,Fup shortfalls due to a problem with
OL,12,FFujitsu's Horizon software.
OL,14,FFour suicides were blamed on the
OL,15,Fscandal.
OL,17,FFormer prime minister Rishi Sunak
OL,18,Fcalled it one of the greatest
OL,19,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,20,Fhistory, with Parliament overturning
OL,21,Fall of the convictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
