OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FThose wrongfully convicted are
OL,8,Feligible for compensation, along with
OL,9,Fmore than 2,750 subpostmasters who
OL,10,Fhave been affected by the scandal but
OL,11,Fnot convicted.
OL,13,FThe larger sum of money is being set
OL,14,Faside for the infected blood scandal,
OL,15,Fwhich has been labelled the "worst
OL,16,Ftreatment disaster in the NHS."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
