OL,3,CReeves promises more than #13bn for
OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FBetween 1970 and 1991 it's thought up
OL,8,Fto 30,000 people were infected with
OL,9,FHIV and Hepatitis C after they were
OL,10,Ftreated with contaminated blood often
OL,11,Fbought from the US.
OL,13,FThose affected by the scandal are
OL,14,Fsplit into two groups.
OL,16,FThe first group are people with
OL,17,Fhaemophilia - experts believe 1,250
OL,18,Fpeople contracted HIV and Hepatitis C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
