OL,4,Cinfected blood and Horizon scandal
OL,5,Cvictims
OL,7,FTwo-thirds then died of AIDS-related
OL,8,Fillnesses, with an unknown amount
OL,9,Ftransferring HIV to their partners.
OL,11,FThe second group were those given
OL,12,Fblood transfusions after childbirth or
OL,13,Fsurgery - 27,000 of whom were infected
OL,14,Fwith Hepatitis C.
OL,16,FIn total, more than 3,000 people are
OL,17,Fknown to have died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
