OL,7,FMany of those who were infected had to
OL,8,Fgive up their jobs and live on
OL,9,Fbenefits because of health problems
OL,10,Fand many of these are now entitled to
OL,11,Fcompensation.
OL,13,FThe average package is expected to be
OL,14,Faround #100,000 but some are set to
OL,15,Freceive much more.
